HEADWORD: Respecting
<hw>Re*spect"ing</hw>, <pos>prep.</pos> <def>With regard or relation to;
regarding; concerning; <as>as, <ex>respecting</ex> his conduct there is
but one opinion</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
